{"tid":1544771,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"各手足小心大搜捕 唔係比狗送去新屋嶺都冇人知","createTime":"2019-09-05T16:19:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-05T16:46:13.000Z","uid":309888,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"9bc86c6f65319e45a37a26ebf43601b2e20199c0","tid":1544771,"uid":309888,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T16:19:04.000Z","msg":"P牌 有一手料見到想同大家講<br />\n琴日夜晚一點幾嗰陣 喺屋企樓下食緊煙<br />\n然後無啦啦有架冇開燈既狗車 停咗喺我屋企樓下<br />\n然後三個軍裝 兩個著背心既便衣(拎住防爆圓盾) 走咗上我棟樓 咁嗰刻緊係嚇到瀨屎 因為有發開夢嘅習慣 咁我緊係唔敢返上樓啦 之後我坐多大約十分鐘 幾隻狗就夾左個人上車 但我相信嗰位義士 失驚無神俾人撳鐘應該搵唔到律師或者朋友幫手 然後靜雞雞比狗拘捕左 嗰刻好想幫佢但我得自己一個同埋有咁多狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 想像唔到如果義士如果自己一個住真係會被消失 冇人知<br />\n所以發過夢既大家真係要小心啲 同埋做好準備 <br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><strong><strong>光復香港時代革命<br />\n五大訴求缺一不可</strong></strong></strong></span></strong>"},{"pid":"7cdfe2f2eacde7e41d697eed2ee636ac8b61a933","tid":1544771,"uid":309888,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T16:20:08.000Z","msg":"推上去比多啲手足知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"975b96683d3863e240435d197fab78be72615575","tid":1544771,"uid":309888,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T16:20:32.000Z","msg":"P牌推唔郁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b82fda4af90628ff241c9a6d7afad3c35a35e9a9","tid":1544771,"uid":79382,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T16:21:42.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"310ac587f10f67becdf16f92513b18f49efc6017","tid":1544771,"uid":117906,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T16:22:26.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"fo